---
title: Chicken, Chorizo and Pepper Fajita Bowl with Coriander Rice, Tomato Salsa and Soured Cream
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Chicken, Chorizo and Pepper Fajita Bowl in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
